---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer" description="AnglerSpecs disclaimer — calculators are for planning purposes only.">
  <div class="panel-head">
    <div>
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <article class="guide">
    <p>Calculators on this site are estimates for planning purposes only. They do not replace your boat's capacity plate, owner's manual, manufacturer specifications, or your own judgment on the water. Where a calculator references a federal regulation (such as 33 CFR 183.53), always verify against the current text of the regulation and your boat's actual documentation before making safety-relevant decisions.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
